TopicTitle: Module manager has found 4 warnings: How to fix?

Articles.Content:
Recently, I installed a bunch of mods with CKAN and now I get a message on the loading screen saying "Module manager has found 4 warnings". 

I dont know what is causing it since I installed the dependencies for mods. My guess was that it was because of some kind of conflict between a couple mods. I havent checked my log but If you want to check the log yourself click here. if you need to check my mods list click here
it appears there is an issue with EVE, SCANsat, CC_RemoteTech, and Restock. I dont know what the issue is but its something because it was complaining about it in the log
